snippet: At least nine people were killed and 10 others wounded near a hotel in the town of Galkayo, a police official said.
abstract: Shabab militant group claims responsibility for suicide bombing in central Somalia that killed at least nine people.
lead_paragraph: At least nine people were killed and 10 others wounded near a hotel in the town of Galkayo, a police official said.
